display.contentTemplate:
• Pending : require user action (approval, submit, Buyer review)

  • Faulted : an error occurred during Workflow execution

  • Unrecoverable : The record (PR, PO, Invoice, …) may have been deleted. Kind of Orphean workflow instance.

$Company = $scope.displayName.split('-')[1].split(' ')[1]
$AppCode = $scope.displayName.split(' ')[0] 
$AppName = $scope.displayName

if ($AppName.Contains('EU')) {$dc = 'eu'}
elseif  ($AppName.Contains('AM')) {$dc = 'am'}  
else{     switch ($Company)
        {
            CompanyName1 {  $dc ='eu'}
            CompanyName2 {  $dc ='am'}
        }
}

if ($AppName.Contains('TEST')) {$env = 'tst'}
elseif  ($AppName.Contains('TRAIN')) {$env = 'trn'}
elseif  ($AppName.Contains('STAGE')){$env = 'stg'}
elseif  ($AppName.Contains('PROD')) {$env = 'prd'}
else {$env = 'prd'}  

$ServerInstance= $dbAlias+'.'+$AppCode+'.'+$env+'.'+$dc+'.'+$Domain+','+$DBPortNumber
$DatabaseName='YourDBName'

$SQLQuery = "
declare @trackingstatus table
(
	Id int,
	Name nvarchar(50),
	State nvarchar(20)
)

insert into @trackingstatus values (0, 'Pending', '');
insert into @trackingstatus values (1, 'Completed', '');
insert into @trackingstatus values (2, 'Cancelled', '');
insert into @trackingstatus values (3, 'Faulted', 'Warning');
insert into @trackingstatus values (4, 'Unrecoverable', 'Critical');

declare @TableId table
(
	Id int,
	Name nvarchar(50)
)
insert into @TableId values (340, 'PurchLine')
insert into @TableId values (345, 'PurchTable')
insert into @TableId values (1209, 'CustInvoiceTable')
insert into @TableId values (1425, 'VendInvoiceInfoTable')
insert into @TableId values (1430, 'VendInvoiceInfoLine')
insert into @TableId values (1551, 'PurchReqTable')
insert into @TableId values (1555, 'PurchReqLine')

select 
		WT.Name,
		ts.Name as WF_STATUS,
		max(ts.State) as State,
		ti.Name as ContextTable
		, count(1) as Counter
  
	from WORKFLOWTABLE WT
	left join WORKFLOWVERSIONTABLE WVT with (nolock)
		on WVT.WORKFLOWTABLE = WT.RECID
		left join WORKFLOWTRACKINGSTATUSTABLE WTST with (nolock)
		on WTST.WORKFLOWVERSIONTABLE = WVT.RECID
	inner join @trackingstatus ts on ts.Id = wtst.TRACKINGSTATUS
	inner join @TableId ti on ti.Id = wtst.CONTEXTTABLEID
	where WTST.TRACKINGSTATUS in (0,3,4)
	group by WT.Name, ts.Name, ti.Name
"  
  
  #Create a Connection to SQL Server
$sqlConn = New-Object System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection
$sqlConn.ConnectionString = "Server=$ServerInstance;Integrated Security=true;Initial Catalog=$DatabaseName"
$sqlConn.Open()

#Get our command pipeline set up
$sqlcmd = $sqlConn.CreateCommand()
$sqlcmd = New-Object System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand
$sqlcmd.Connection = $sqlConn
$sqlcmd.CommandText = $SQLQuery

#Create the Data Adapter
$adp = New-Object System.Data.SqlClient.SqlDataAdapter $sqlcmd

#Create and fill the DataSet
$ds = New-Object System.Data.DataSet
$t = $adp.Fill($ds)

#Save our SQL Results
$SQLResults = $ds.Tables[0].Rows
$Results = @($SQLResults)

$Results

$DatabaseName='YourDBName'

$SQLQuery = "
declare @trackingstatus table
(
	Id int,
	Name nvarchar(50),
	State nvarchar(20)
)

insert into @trackingstatus values (0, 'Pending', '');
insert into @trackingstatus values (1, 'Completed', '');
insert into @trackingstatus values (2, 'Cancelled', '');
insert into @trackingstatus values (3, 'Faulted', 'Warning');
insert into @trackingstatus values (4, 'Unrecoverable', 'Critical');

declare @TableId table
(
	Id int,
	Name nvarchar(50)
)
insert into @TableId values (340, 'PurchLine')
insert into @TableId values (345, 'PurchTable')
insert into @TableId values (1209, 'CustInvoiceTable')
insert into @TableId values (1425, 'VendInvoiceInfoTable')
insert into @TableId values (1430, 'VendInvoiceInfoLine')
insert into @TableId values (1551, 'PurchReqTable')
insert into @TableId values (1555, 'PurchReqLine')

select 
		CONCAT(WT.Name,' - ',ts.Name) As Name,ts.Name,
		max(ts.State) as State,
		ti.Name as ContextTable
		, count(1) as Counter
  
	from WORKFLOWTABLE WT
	left join WORKFLOWVERSIONTABLE WVT with (nolock)
		on WVT.WORKFLOWTABLE = WT.RECID
		left join WORKFLOWTRACKINGSTATUSTABLE WTST with (nolock)
		on WTST.WORKFLOWVERSIONTABLE = WVT.RECID
	inner join @trackingstatus ts on ts.Id = wtst.TRACKINGSTATUS
	inner join @TableId ti on ti.Id = wtst.CONTEXTTABLEID
	where WTST.TRACKINGSTATUS in (0,3,4)
	group by WT.Name, ts.Name, ti.Name
    ORDER BY Counter DESC
"  
  
  #Create a Connection to SQL Server
$sqlConn = New-Object System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection
$sqlConn.ConnectionString = "Server=$ServerInstance;Integrated Security=true;Initial Catalog=$DatabaseName"
$sqlConn.Open()

#Get our command pipeline set up
$sqlcmd = $sqlConn.CreateCommand()
$sqlcmd = New-Object System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand
$sqlcmd.Connection = $sqlConn
$sqlcmd.CommandText = $SQLQuery

#Create the Data Adapter
$adp = New-Object System.Data.SqlClient.SqlDataAdapter $sqlcmd

#Create and fill the DataSet
$ds = New-Object System.Data.DataSet
$t = $adp.Fill($ds)

#Save our SQL Results
$SQLResults = $ds.Tables[0].Rows
$Results = @($SQLResults)

$Results
